	<article id="post-3150" class="post-3150 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-big-brother category-civil-liberties category-current-affairs category-democracy category-drugs-2 category-economics category-extradition category-intelligence category-ip category-it category-law category-leap category-national-security category-organisations category-politics category-prohibition-2 category-science category-spies category-surveillance category-tv category-war-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-festival tag-geeks tag-intelligence-2 tag-netherlands tag-nl tag-observe-hack-make tag-ohm tag-police-2 tag-spies-2 tag-surveillance-2 tag-whistleblowers-2 tag-wikileaks">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/07/dutch-festival-ohm-observe-hack-make.html" title="Permalink to Dutch festival OHM — Observe, Hack, Make" rel="bookmark">Dutch festival <span class="caps">OHM</span> — Observe, Hack, Make</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/07/dutch-festival-ohm-observe-hack-make.html" title="21:52" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-07-30T21:52:22+00:00" pubdate>July 30, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/07/dutch-festival-ohm-observe-hack-make.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Today I am limber­ing up to attend the Dutch geek fest­ival, Observe Hack Make (<a href="https://program.ohm2013.org/"><span class="caps">OHM</span> 2013</a>). A lot of talks from whis­tleblowers, sci­ent­ists, geeks, futur­ists and bleed­ing edge tech people. The visionaries?</p>
<p>You decide — all talks will be live streamed and avail­able after­wards. Enjoy!</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
