				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/festival" rel="tag">festival</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/geeks" rel="tag">geeks</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/netherlands" rel="tag">Netherlands</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/nl" rel="tag">NL</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/observe-hack-make" rel="tag">Observe Hack Make</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/ohm" rel="tag">OHM</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/police-2" rel="tag">police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
